  "detailed_description": "\"The seal of ancient dungeon had broken,countless of monsters escape from dungeon.<br>The warrior of chick kingdom named \"\"Giant\"\" decide to go deep to the dungeon and reseal it.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Giant\" moves back a lot when shooting because of strong recoil. Since \"Giant\" doesn't move fast, you need to learn and use this recoil to avoid dangers. This means you will quickly shift positions after shooting to escape tricky and dangerous spots.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The weapon of \"Giant\" has a feature is that it can cause fatal damage to enemies at close range. You can use this weapon's feature defeat enemies quickly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Giant\" dies with just one hit, making it pretty hard. But don't worry! The more you play and practice, the better you'll understand how the game works and find ways to win. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "\"The seal of ancient dungeon had broken,countless of monsters escape from dungeon.<br>The warrior of chick kingdom named \"\"Giant\"\" decide to go deep to the dungeon and reseal it.\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/0b543a5851d554dc5d7c599ba6f279d8.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Giant\" moves back a lot when shooting because of strong recoil. Since \"Giant\" doesn't move fast, you need to learn and use this recoil to avoid dangers. This means you will quickly shift positions after shooting to escape tricky and dangerous spots.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/4024d976610fe07778337fdb868adede.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The weapon of \"Giant\" has a feature is that it can cause fatal damage to enemies at close range. You can use this weapon's feature defeat enemies quickly.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/b7ab3098925f8c2bb51999334bbf8d50.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Giant\" dies with just one hit, making it pretty hard. But don't worry! The more you play and practice, the better you'll understand how the game works and find ways to win. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.poster.avif?t=1751334690\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.webm?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2860380/extras/2b1b3848aa8be378218954cb1f8a6e6d.mp4?t=1751334690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
